# Emotional Cycles
# ============================================================================

lov → los → lov
# love → loss → love
# Grief transforms love; love after loss is deeper

hop → fea → hop
# hope → fear → hope
# Courage is hope that has faced fear

joy → sad → joy
# joy → sadness → joy
# True joy includes memory of sorrow

cal → ang → cal
# calm → anger → calm
# Peace after conflict is earned peace

tru → dou → tru
# trust → doubt → trust
# Tested trust is stronger trust

